snippet.title: Six? | Lurking in the Dark | Lunacy Playthrough, No Commentary #Lunacy #LurkingintheDark
snippet.description:
Lurking in the Dark is a puzzle horror game made by kotob and SamirKazah as well as the Winner of GMTK Game Jam 2019. 

Game Description: 
- Climb the tower, light the candles, and revive the Dark One.

Game Info: https://asheraryam.itch.io/lurking-in-the-dark
